  "description": {
    "zh": "好吧，我现在有时间了。最近有一些新推出的收藏手办，非常特别。没人知道它们来自哪里，但它们既值钱又稀有，而我想要它们！明白我的意思吗？我想要每种一个，它们都是独一无二的。我已经知道该联系谁了，这些手办对我的买家来说价值连城，而且他很急，所以请快点行动。",
    "en": "Okay I got some time now. There are these new collectible figures going around, special stuff. Nobody knows where they came from but they are valuable and rare, and I want them!\n\nUnderstand what I am saying? I want one of each, they are one of a kind. I already know who to contact, they are worth a fortune to my buyer and he is impatient so hurry up."
  },
